  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You've mastered fighting without sight, finding a home in the darkness that your enemies fear. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Once per round, when a creature would have disadvantage on an attack roll against you due to being blinded, they must reroll one of the dice once.</li>\n<li>Once per round, when you would have advantage on an attack roll against a creature that is blinded, you can reroll one of the dice once.</li>\n<li>You gain blindsight out to a number of feet equal to 5 x your proficiency bonus. If you already have blindsight, it instead increases by a number of feet equal to 5 x your proficiency bonus.</li></ul>",
